# TailAdmin Dashboard Rules

## Stack & Versions
- Tailwind CSS v4
- TailAdmin free tier component system
- React / Next.js (preferred), or Vue / SvelteKit if project uses it
- ApexCharts for all data visualizations
- Flatpickr for date pickers

## Folder Structure
Follow TailAdmin's structure:
```
src/
├── components/
│   ├── Charts/        # ApexCharts wrappers
│   ├── Dashboard/     # Stat cards, summaries
│   ├── Header/        # Top navbar
│   ├── Sidebar/       # Side navigation
│   ├── Tables/        # Data tables
│   └── ui/            # Buttons, badges, modals, forms
├── layout/
│   └── DefaultLayout.tsx  # Main shell: Sidebar + Header + Content
├── pages/             # Route-level pages
└── types/             # Shared TypeScript types
```

## Layout Shell
Always use the DefaultLayout wrapper for dashboard pages:
```tsx
<DefaultLayout>
  <PageContent />
</DefaultLayout>
```

The DefaultLayout must include:
- Persistent sidebar on `lg:` and above
- Collapsible hamburger sidebar on mobile
- Fixed top header bar on all breakpoints
- Bottom padding to avoid content clipping on mobile

## Responsive Sidebar Pattern
```tsx
// Sidebar: hidden on mobile, visible on desktop
<aside className="fixed left-0 top-0 z-9999 flex h-screen w-72 flex-col
  overflow-y-hidden bg-black duration-300 ease-linear
  lg:translate-x-0 -translate-x-full">
  ...
</aside>

// Overlay for mobile sidebar
<div className="fixed inset-0 z-999 bg-black/80 lg:hidden" />
```

## Color Tokens
Use TailAdmin's design tokens — never hardcode hex values:
| Token | Usage |
|---|---|
| `bg-white dark:bg-boxdark` | Card / panel backgrounds |
| `bg-whiten` | Page background (light) |
| `text-black dark:text-white` | Primary text |
| `text-bodydark1`, `text-bodydark2` | Secondary / muted text |
| `border-stroke dark:border-strokedark` | All borders and dividers |
| `bg-primary` | Brand blue — buttons, active states |
| `text-meta-3` | Success / green indicators |
| `text-meta-1` | Danger / red indicators |
| `text-meta-6` | Warning / yellow indicators |

## Dark Mode
- Always implement dark mode with Tailwind's `dark:` variant
- Never use CSS overrides for dark mode
- Toggle by adding/removing the `dark` class on `<html>`
- Store preference in localStorage key `color-theme`

## Stat Card Pattern
```tsx
<div className="rounded-sm border border-stroke bg-white px-7.5 py-6
  shadow-default dark:border-strokedark dark:bg-boxdark">
  <div className="flex h-11.5 w-11.5 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-meta-2">
    <Icon className="fill-primary" />
  </div>
  <div className="mt-4">
    <h4 className="text-title-md font-bold text-black dark:text-white">$3,456</h4>
    <span className="text-sm font-medium text-bodydark2">Total Revenue</span>
  </div>
</div>
```

## Tables
- Use TailAdmin's table structure with `border-stroke` borders
- Always include `overflow-x-auto` wrapper on mobile for horizontal scroll
- Stripe rows with `hover:bg-gray-3 dark:hover:bg-meta-4`
- Never use third-party table libraries unless the project already has one

## Charts (ApexCharts)
- Wrap every chart in a `<div className="rounded-sm border border-stroke bg-white ... dark:bg-boxdark">`
- Always pass `theme: { mode: isDark ? 'dark' : 'light' }` to ApexCharts options
- Use TailAdmin color palette in `colors: ['#3C50E0', '#80CAEE']`
- Chart containers must be responsive: `width: '100%'`, fixed `height`

## Forms & Inputs
```tsx
<input className="w-full rounded border-[1.5px] border-stroke bg-transparent
  px-5 py-3 font-normal text-black outline-none transition
  focus:border-primary active:border-primary
  dark:border-form-strokedark dark:bg-form-input dark:text-white
  dark:focus:border-primary" />
```

## Buttons
```tsx
// Primary
<button className="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md
  bg-primary px-10 py-4 text-center font-medium text-white
  hover:bg-opacity-90">
  Save
</button>

// Outline
<button className="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md
  border border-primary px-10 py-4 text-center font-medium text-primary
  hover:bg-primary hover:text-white">
  Cancel
</button>
```

## Typography Scale
| Class | Usage |
|---|---|
| `text-title-2xl` | Page hero numbers |
| `text-title-xl` | Section headings |
| `text-title-md` | Card titles, stat values |
| `text-title-sm` | Subsection labels |
| `text-sm` | Body, table content |
| `text-xs` | Badges, captions, metadata |

## Spacing
- Use TailAdmin's extended spacing: `px-7.5`, `py-6`, `gap-7.5`
- Card inner padding: `p-6` on mobile, `p-7.5` on `sm:` and up
- Grid gaps: `gap-4 md:gap-6 2xl:gap-7.5`

## Page Grid Layout
```tsx
<div className="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-6
  xl:grid-cols-4 2xl:gap-7.5">
  {/* Stat cards */}
</div>

<div className="mt-4 grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 md:mt-6 md:gap-6 2xl:mt-7.5 2xl:gap-7.5">
  {/* Charts: span 8 cols, sidebar panel: span 4 cols */}
</div>
```

## Do's
- Always derive colors from TailAdmin tokens, not Tailwind defaults
- Always pair every `bg-white` with `dark:bg-boxdark`
- Always wrap page content in `DefaultLayout`
- Use ApexCharts for any new chart — don't mix in Chart.js or Recharts
- Keep sidebar nav items inside `<SidebarItem>` component

## Don'ts
- Don't hardcode hex colors anywhere in JSX or CSS
- Don't add a new UI library without checking if TailAdmin already has the component
- Don't use `fixed` positioning inside page content — only in Header/Sidebar
- Don't skip the `dark:` variant on any background, text, or border class
- Don't use `px-4` on cards — TailAdmin uses `px-7.5` for card padding
